clipsnap (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of ClipSnap
  * Features:
    - Modern area screenshot capture with premium UI
    - Comprehensive clipboard history management  
    - Global keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+Alt+S for screenshot, Alt+H for history)
    - Automatic startup and system integration
    - SQLite-based storage with thumbnail generation
    - Cross-desktop environment compatibility
    - Enhanced coordinate mapping and high-DPI support
    - Professional visual design with smooth animations
  * Improvements over previous versions:
    - Fixed screenshot accuracy issues
    - Eliminated unwanted overlay artifacts in captures
    - Added premium visual styling and animations
    - Enhanced multi-monitor support
    - Improved error handling and user feedback

 -- ClipSnap Team <team@clipsnap.com>  Sun, 16 Feb 2026 12:00:00 +0000